{
  "id": "adv_main_02_07_04",
  "title": "東京編2章9話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……やっと帰ってこられた\nとんでもない会議だった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh* We finally got out of there.\nWhat a crazy meeting that was.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.633333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2599.9999999999995,
          "startTime": 7.233333333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2599.999999999996,
          "startTime": 7.23333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 7.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、{user}さん！\nお帰りなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! {user}-san!\nWelcome back!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 10.6333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "会議、どうでしたか？\nだいぶ疲れているようですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How did the meeting go?\nYou look awfully tired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 15.866666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、会議の目的はなんだったの？\nあの人が意味もなく他の事務所を巻き込むとは思えない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What even was the purpose of the meeting?\nI doubt that woman would rope in other agencies for no reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 23.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ま、待ってくれ、ちゃんと説明するから……\n先に落ち着かせてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wait a minute. I’ll explain everything.\nJust let me calm down first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 28.6666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ、はやる気持ちは分かるけどさ\nさとみなんか、見てみなよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I get that you’re impatience‚\nbut just look at Satomi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 34.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "きょうぎかい……ひめのさん……こわわわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meeting… Himeno-san… freaky…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 39.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 43.666666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "かわいそうに……よほど辛い目にあったのね\n落ち着いてからでいいから、詳しく聞かせてもらえる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Poor thing. She must have really been traumatized.\nTake all the time you need to calm down. Then‚ will you give us the details?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 48.0666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 48.0666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 48.233333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 48.233333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-krk001.m4a",
      "text": "皆様もご存じの通り、先日、バンプロダクション社長\n朝倉恭一氏が、横領の容疑で逮捕されました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As you all know‚ a few days ago‚ Van Productions’s company president‚\nKyoichi Asakura‚ was arrested on suspicion of embezzlement.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-krk002.m4a",
      "text": "世間では様々な意見が飛び交い、その大半が\nアイドル業界に対する非常にネガティブな批判です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Various opinions are flying around amongst the public‚\nmost of which are terribly negative criticisms of the idol industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 66.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "あの……進行役、姫野さんなんですね\nやっぱり、この会議の音頭を取ったのって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… the facilitator of this meeting is Himeno-san‚ right?\nSo I guess she was the one who set it up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 73.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、姫野さんで間違いないだろうな\n彼女の狙いがなんなのか、見定めるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. It had to be Himeno-san.\nWatch closely and try to see what her motive is here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 81.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 81.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-krk003.m4a",
      "text": "このままでは、アイドル業界は衰退の一途を辿ります\nそんな窮地に立たされた今だからこそ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At this rate‚ the idol industry will fall into decline.\nAnd it is because we are currently in hot water",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-krk004.m4a",
      "text": "私は、慣習ですませてきた業界の在り方に\nメスを入れるべく、二つのプロジェクトを提案します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "that I wish to propose two projects which I hope will clean up\nthis industry’s customary practices and mold it into what it should be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-krk005.m4a",
      "text": "一つは、この場にいる大手事務所の皆様にも\n加入していただく、アイドル業界を統べる組織――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Firstly‚ I wish to invite all the big talent agencies here in attendance\nto join me in founding a new organization to guide the idol industry:",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.63333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-krk006.m4a",
      "text": "アイドル・エンターテインメント・アソシエーション\nI.E.A.の設立です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the Idol Entertainment Association‚\nor IEA.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 111.5
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 111.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "業界を統べる組織……って、何？\n闇の組織的な？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A new organization to guide the idol industry… What’s that?\nIs it like an evil organization?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "いわゆる『協会』のことでしょうね\n確かに今まで、アイドル業界には存在しませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it’s what you’d call a “society.”\nIt’s true. The idol industry has had nothing like it up until now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "世間のネガティブなイメージを払拭するために\n団結しましょうってことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it like‚ let’s unite together to help clean up\nour negative image with the public?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "理想を言えば。でも、事務所同士の結びつきを強くして\n互いの動向を監視し合う、という目的もあると思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ideally‚ yes. But I think her secondary goal in founding such a society is to\nstrengthen the bonds between agencies so they can police each other’s activity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（それだけなら、提案としてはまだ妥当だった……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If it were just that‚ I could still consider it a valid proposal. However…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 147.33333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 147.66666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_04-krk007.m4a",
      "text": "そしてもう一つの提案は、そのI.E.A.に\n加入している事務所によって運営する――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My other proposal is that all agencies\nbelonging to the I.E.A. would help run",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
